      *@   WK-AREA 및　프로그램파라미터　초기화
           INITIALIZE WK-AREA
      *               SQLIO
                      YCDBSQLA-CA

      *@  출력영역　및　결과코드　초기화
           INITIALIZE XDJL4150-OUT
                      XDJL4150-RETURN
           .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.
