      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-VALIDATION-RTN.

      *@   1 DC필수입력파라미터 검증
      *@   1.1 처리구분코드체크
      *@   실행조건 : 입력.처리구분코드=01
      *@   처리내용 : 에러처리
           IF XDJL4150-I-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01
      *@에러메세지 : 처리구분오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
              #ERROR CO-B3000070 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF

           .
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  업무처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.

      *@1  국별수기국적조회
           PERFORM S3100-QJL4150-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3100-QJL4150-CALL-EXT
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 국별수기국적조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-QJL4150-CALL-RTN.

      *@   변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL4150-IN

      *@    변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL4150-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월일(전영업일)
           MOVE JICOM-BF-BZOPR-YMD
             TO XQJL4150-I-BASE-YMD

      *@   계좌번호 - NEXT KEY
      *@   자동거래일경우 NEXT KEY 처리한다
           IF BICOM-DSCN-TRAN-DSTCD = CO-CHA-1 OR CO-CHA-2

           #USRLOG  "=================================================="
           #USRLOG  "*                 NEXT    KEY                    *"
           #USRLOG  "=================================================="

              MOVE BOCOM-BF-TDK-INFO-CTNT
                TO WK-BF-KEY
              MOVE WK-BF-ACNO
                TO XQJL4150-I-ACNO

           #USRLOG  " WK-BF-ACNO : " WK-BF-ACNO
           #USRLOG  "=================================================="
           END-IF

      *@1.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL4150 XQJL4150-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블SELECT오류입니다.
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE
           IF DBSQL-SELECT-CNT > CO-MAX-CNT
              MOVE CO-MAX-CNT
                TO XDJL4150-O-PRSNT-NOITM1
           ELSE
              MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
                TO XDJL4150-O-PRSNT-NOITM1
           END-IF

           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4150-O-PRSNT-NOITM1

      *            계좌번호
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-ACNO (WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-ACNO (WK-I)

      *            ISO국가코드
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-ISO-NATNL-CD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-ISO-NATNL-CD(WK-I)

      *            USD한도
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-USD-CLAM(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-USD-CLAM(WK-I)

      *            ISO국가코드2
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-ISO-NATNL-CD2(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-ISO-NATNL-CD2(WK-I)

      *            등록년월일
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-REGI-YMD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-REGI-YMD(WK-I)

      *            등록직원번호
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-REGI-EMPID(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-REGI-EMPID(WK-I)

      *            등록직원명
               MOVE  XQJL4150-O-REGI-EMNM(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4150-O-REGI-EMNM(WK-I)

           END-PERFORM

           #USRLOG  "=================================================="
           #USRLOG  " DBSQL-SELECT-CNT : " DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
           #USRLOG  " XQJL4150-O-ACNO(100) : " XQJL4150-O-ACNO(100)
           #USRLOG  "=================================================="

           IF DBSQL-SELECT-CNT > CO-NUM-100
              MOVE XQJL4150-O-ACNO(100)
                TO WK-AF-ACNO
              #DSCNTR 2 WK-AF-KEY
           END-IF

           .
       S3100-QJL4150-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

